# ================================================================

### 77. List all sections (filter by dept/semester/year)
GET {{base}}/sections?dept_id=DEPARTMENT_ID&year=3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 78. Get section by ID
GET {{base}}/sections/SECTION_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 79. Create a section
