Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Genius",
  "dept_id": "DEPARTMENT_ID",
  "semester_id": "SEMESTER_ID",
  "year": 3,
  "strength": 60,
  "subjects": []
}

###

### 80. Update section — assign specific subjects
PATCH {{base}}/sections/SECTION_ID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
